text: Consider the following y86 program 1: 2: irmovq 1, %rax 3: irmovq 7, %rbx 4: irmovg 1, %rcx 5: 6: loop_start: 7: rrmovq %rax, %rdi 8: addq %rcx, %rax 9: rrmovq %rbx, %rbp 10: subq %srdi, %rbp 11: jle loop_end 12: jmp loop_start 13: 14: loop_end: 15: andq %ril2, %ril3 16: mrmovq 0x44c(%rl3), %rdi 17: divqg %ril2, %rile 18: mrmovq 0x10c3(%rll), %ri2 19: Assume a pipelined implemention with no forwarding and a branch prediction algorithm that predicts taken for backward branches and not taken for forward branches.
